summary:
- **Substantial Holder Change**: Mark Gregory Kerr & associates transferred 349,133,188 FPOs (11.00% voting power) and 189,000,000 options (AVEOA, 8.80% voting power) from Lindmark Inv Staff S/F A/C to Paradyce Pty Ltd on 19 June 2025.  
- **No change in total ownership**: Total voting power remains unchanged (11.00% for FPOs, 8.80% for options).  
- **Nature of change**: Inter-account transfer (no consideration involved).  

No material trading or capital markets impact identified.
